For example, he could read hearts.

00:23:18.150 --> 00:23:21.150
The scriptures describe an occasion

00:23:21.150 --> 00:23:27.150
when Jesus responded to a man's thoughts rather than to his words.

00:23:27.150 --> 00:23:32.150
Do you think Jesus' ability to know what his audience was thinking

00:23:32.150 --> 00:23:39.150
and feeling enhanced his effectiveness as he shared his gift?

